WWW::UsePerl::Journal
=====================

DESCRIPTION

An all round journal tool for use.perl addicts. Will access journal entries
for a specific user, or the latest 30 postings, or retrieve a specific
journal entry. Can also post into a specific user's journal.

DEPENDENCIES

The distribution requires the following modules:

  LWP::UserAgent        => 0,
  Time::Piece           => 1.07,
  Test::Simple          => 0.40,
  Test::More            => 0,

CHANGES

See the Changes file for a list of updates to the distribution.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

